      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#159A9C] mb-3">
            Kruszywa i Piasek:
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 font-medium list-disc list-inside">
            <li>Piasek pukany (0-2 mm) - do wylewek i murowania</li>
